@tijoparacka We also need to annotate the constructor. The correct version should be the following

``` scala
@Since("1.2.0")
class BinaryClassificationEvaluator @Since("1.4.0") (@Since("1.4.0") override val uid: String)
```

Note that `uid` is not public in 1.2 and 1.3.
